Pampered Pup Spa & Salon\",\"businessType\":\"Dog Park\",\"description\":\"If you're looking for the ultimate wag-worthy social hub in [Toms River](/cities/toms-river-nj), look no further than Pampered Pup Spa & Salon. This vibrant community destination has earned a reputation as the \\\"place to be\\\" for local pet parents who want more than just a walk—they want a meetup. Boasting a solid 4.5-star rating from 21 reviews, the park radiates a welcoming energy where tails never stop wagging and neighbors become friends. Whether you're there for a quick playdate or a long afternoon of socializing, the atmosphere is always buzzing with positivity.\\n\\nAt Pampered Pup Spa & Salon, the focus is on connection. The layout encourages interaction, making it easy for pups to find playmates while owners chat on the sidelines. It’s not just a facility; it’s a social pillar of the Toms River scene, offering a safe, clean, and joyous environment where every visitor feels like a VIP. For a fun, friendly, and community-centered experience, this spot is a local favorite.\",\"slug\":\"pampered-pup-spa-salon\",\"address\":\"1188 NJ-166\",\"street\":\"1188 NJ-166\",\"city\":\"Toms River\",\"state\":\"NJ\",\"zipCode\":\"08753\",\"full_address\":\"1188 NJ-166, Toms River, NJ 08753, USA\",\"latitude\":39.98170530000001,\"longitude\":-74.21009579999999,\"googlePlaceId\":\"ChIJrSAVhYWdwYkRDBN7nv-vyIQ\",\"phone\":\"\",\"website\":\"\",\"photos\":null,\"rating\":4.5,\"reviewCount\":21,\"openingHours\":{\"Monday\":\"11:00 AM – 5:00 PM\",\"Tuesday\":\"10:00 AM – 3:00 PM\",\"Wednesday\":\"10:00 AM – 3:00 PM\",\"Thursday\":\"10:00 AM – 3:00 PM\",\"Friday\":\"10:00 AM – 5:00 PM\",\"Saturday\":\"8:30 AM – 6:00 PM\",\"Sunday\":\"11:00 AM – 5:00 PM\"},\"amenities\":{\"Onsite services\":true,\"Indoor facilities\":true,\"Professional staff\":true,\"Climate controlled\":true,\"Wheelchair accessible entrance\":false,\"Parking available\":true,\"Easy access\":true},\"pricing\":{\"pricingSource\":\"websi