"text-sm text-white/50\",\"children\":\"IndoorDogPark is a participant in the Amazon Services LLC Associates Program, an affiliate advertising program designed to provide a means for sites to earn advertising fees by advertising and linking to Amazon.com. As an Amazon Associate I earn from qualifying purchases.\"}]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"footer-bottom\",\"children\":[\"$L21\",\"$L22\"]}]]}]}]\na:[\"$\",\"$L23\",null,{}]\nb:[\"$\",\"$L24\",null,{\"children\":[\"$\",\"$25\",null,{\"name\":\"Next.MetadataOutlet\",\"children\":\"$@26\"}]}]\n12:[\"$\",\"span\",\"Data refreshed weekly\",{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"i\",null,{\"className\":\"bi bi-sparkles\"}],\" \",\"Data refreshed weekly\"]}]\n13:[\"$\",\"span\",\"Live availability coming soon\",{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"i\",null,{\"className\":\"bi bi-sparkles\"}],\" \",\"Live availability coming soon\"]}]\n14:[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"city-hero-visual\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"hero-image-card\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"$L27\",null,{\"src\":\"/images/cities/toms-river/hero.webp\",\"alt\":\"Toms River dog park landscape\",\"fill\":true,\"priority\":true,\"sizes\":\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 540px\",\"unoptimized\":true}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"hero-image-gradient\"}]]}]}]\n15:[\"$\",\"$L28\",null,{\"city\":\"Toms River\",\"state\":\"NJ\"}]\n2a:T429,Serious about your pup's fitness and focus? Best Friend Dog Training in [Toms River](/cities/toms-river-nj) delivers a top-tier environment designed for activity and engagement. Rated 5 stars by a community of 19 disciplined dog owners, this facility is built on the logic of \"constructive play.\" It’s not just about running around; it’s about mental stimulation, clear boundaries, and a structured space where dogs can burn off energy productively.\n\nThe layout at Best Friend Dog Training is ideal for training exercises, recall practice, and agility drills. The grounds are kept in peak condition to ensure safety during high-intensity play, and the respectful community of regulars understands the value of good canine etiquette. Whether you are working on commands or just need a reliable space for vigorous exercise, this facility provides the professional-grade consistency that serious dog owners demand.\n\nFor more details, visit the [official property website](https://bestfriendsdogtrainingnj.com/) to learn more about their services and updated hours.2b:T460,If you're looking for the ultimate wag-worthy social hub in [40 Main St](/cities/40-main-st-nj), look no further than Canine Aesthetic. This vibrant community destination has earned a reputation as the \"place to be\" for local pet parents who want more than just a walk—they want a meetup. Boasting a solid 5-star rating from 15 reviews, the park radiates a welcoming energy where tails never stop wagging and neighbors become friends. Whether you're there for a quick playdate or a long afternoon of socializing, the atmosphere is always buzzing with positivity.\n\nAt Canine Aesthetic, the focus is on connection. The layout encourages interaction, making it easy for pups to find playmates while owners chat on the sidelines. It’s not just a facility; it’s a social pillar of the 40 Main St scene, offering a safe, clean, and joyous environment where every visitor feels like a VIP. For a fun, friendly, and community-centered experience, this spot is a local favorite.\n\nFor more details, visit the [official property website](https://www.canineaesthetic.com/) to learn more about their services and updated hours.2c:T4ae,If you're looking for the ultimate wag-worthy social hub in [Toms River](/cities/toms-river-nj), look no further than Cattus Island County Park. This vibrant community destination has earned a reputation as the \"place to be\" for local pet parents who want more than just a walk—they want a meetup. Boasting a solid 4.7-star rating from 937 reviews, the park radiates a welcoming energy where tails never stop wagging and n